    "description": "<p>For each of twelve statements you do two things: rate your agreement, then say what would change your mind. This is not about whether you are right; it maps the tension between how strongly you hold a belief and how open you are to revising it.</p><p>Inspired by actively open-minded thinking (AOT) scales. Original items.</p>",
