    "privacyNote": "Your answers stay in this browser. The result belongs to you. Sharing is your choice.",
    "disclaimer": "Inspired by actively open-minded thinking (AOT) scales (public domain). Items are original adaptations. This is not a validated psychometric assessment.",
    "startButton": "Map my conviction"
